---
title: Herby Falafel & Tahini Couscous Bowl with Feta Salsa & Toasted Almonds
description: Have a ball with dinner – a ball of lightly spiced chickpeas blended with parsley and coriander, that is! Yep, we’re talking about falafels! With couscous, tahini sauce, flaked almonds and feta salsa, they make a dinner that's got the lot.
